column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec, s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.snMedian, s.zWarning FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.snMedian > #   AND s.class = &&&   AND (subclass LIKE &&&)  AND s.zWarning = #
